content.raw: Hi Jason, To perform the testing correctly, I need to have Update method to be called by Parse method since in my test the init message has been overwritten, this is the only change in effector now. I should also use the latest version in jliang_model branch, please check the latest version I think you forget to add Util.CC to the repository.
